{"tid":2198579,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"Michelle Rodriguez 證實人氣動作大片《Fast & Furious 9》將會飛上「外太空」","createTime":"2020-09-11T12:27:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-12T00:34:51.000Z","uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f8fc722dedc3e4a60ddf885841aa8a385a35b245","tid":2198579,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T12:27:42.000Z","msg":"開播至今已有 20 年之久的美國史詩級動作大片《Fast &amp; Furious》原定在今年推出第九集《Fast &amp; Furious 9》（F9、F9: The Fast Saga、F9 狂野時速、玩命關頭 9），不料因疫情關係現已確定推遲至 2021 年上映。<br />\n<br />\n二月份時，曾率先發布電影首波預告，能看見 Vin Diesel 飾演的 Dominic Toretto 已經組了家庭且有了兒子，但必須面對由 John Cena 飾演的反派角色，而該角色除了偷竊專家、飆速高手，更是「唐老大」的弟弟，勢均力敵的兩組人馬或將透過陸海空三地對決上演無數次的飛車追逐與爆破場面，而更大的驚喜則是 Han 的復活回歸。<br />\n<br />\n近期劇中演員 Michelle Rodriguez 在 Sirius XM 的 The Jess Cagle Show 的節目中被問到，另一演員 Lodacris 曾經說溜嘴《Fast &amp; Furious 9》將會飛上外太空的說法，Michelle Rodriguez 率先驚訝回問大家怎麼知道這件事的，外界不該有人知道此事，當電影延期後大家都忘記保密了。<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;Oh, no way. How did you guys find that out? See what happens? People start talking behind the scenes, man,&rdquo; said Rodriguez. &ldquo;When a movie doesn&rsquo;t come out and forget about it, things get out. Nobody was supposed to know that!&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n爾後，Michelle Rodriguez 另類證實且表示並非由她出演飛出外太空的片段，也順勢稱讚導演 Justin Lin（林詣彬）給予劇中女性角色更為多元的刻畫且擁有更多的發揮空間。《Fast &amp; Furious 9》目前暫定於 2021 年 4 月 2 日正式上映。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hypebeast.com/zh/2020/9/f9-fast-and-furious-saga-confirmed-go-to-space\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhypebeast.com%2Fzh%2F2020%2F9%2Ff9-fast-and-furious-saga-confirmed-go-to-space&d=lPOaXpfFeUboYNX3auI3fqP8PJJZD286lWcuKEclkJo%3D&h=b84422fe\" target=\"_blank\">https://hypebeast.com/zh/2020/9/f9-fast-and-furious-saga-confirmed-go-to-space</a>"},{"pid":"455f31a260d6a5ad20a86aa36775b9eb207b29e8","tid":2198579,"uid":75050,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T12:29:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://starecat.com/content/wp-content/uploads/fast-and-fu